                                        <h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-what-makes-travel-china-with-me-unique">What
                                            Makes TRAVEL CHINA WITH ME Unique?</h2>
                                        <p>Compared to large travel companies, we operate on a smaller scale—but that's
                                            exactly why we offer better value.</p>
                                        <h3 class="wp-block-heading">More Focused</h3>
                                        <p>Over the past few years, I've worked with some brilliant brands including Royal Caribbean, Visit England, Topdeck, Samsung, Yellow Zebra Safaris, Panasonic, Hotels.com, Expedia, Obonjan, TRVL, Movenpick Hotels and icelolly.com</p>
                                        <p>Would you like to work with me? If you have an opportunity you think I'd be interested in or would like to get in touch – please drop an email to contact@stokedtotravel.com to discuss your idea or request further information.</p>
                                        <h3 class="wp-block-heading">Transparent &amp; Clearer Itemized Quote</h3>
                                        <p>My current monthly unique users are 60,000 and I can happily send you a media kit and overview of Google stats, should you need 🙂</p>
                                        <p>At the same time, this transparent pricing structure clearly outlines the
                                            cost breakdown of each service in every city, making it easier for you to
                                            understand how your money is being spent. We provide a detailed list of what
                                            is included and excluded in the quote to avoid any misunderstandings,
                                            ensuring there are no &#8220;hidden costs&#8221; beyond your understanding.
                                        </p>
                                        <h3 class="wp-block-heading">Low Prepayment Deposit</h3>
                                        <p>Unlike other travel companies that ask for large deposits or even full
                                            payment upfront, we totally understand how you might feel when booking
                                            online. That's why we only ask for a <strong>15% deposit</strong> when you
                                            book your trip. The rest can be paid after you arrive in China and have
                                            experienced our top-notch services. If you trust us, we'll trust you even
                                            more and do everything we can to live up to that trust.</p>
                                        <p><em><strong>P.S. </strong>Don't worry about payment when you arrive in China.
                                                We will guide you on <a
                                                    href="https://travelchinawith.me/china-travel-how-tos/how-to-use-alipay-in-china-for-foreigners-the-complete-guide/"
                                                    data-type="page" data-id="2584" target="_blank"
                                                    rel="noreferrer noopener">how to use Alipay</a> for secure and
                                                convenient online payments, whether you want to use a debit or credit
                                                card.</em></p>
                                        <figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="912"
                                                height="684"
                                                src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;912&#039;%20height=&#039;684&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20912%20684&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E"
                                                alt="About" class="wp-image-1058 perfmatters-lazy" title="About 3"
                                                data-src="https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_3996.jpg.webp"
                                                data-srcset="https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_3996.jpg.webp 912w, https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_3996-300x225.jpg.webp 300w"
                                                data-sizes="(max-width: 912px) 100vw, 912px" /><noscript><img
                                                    decoding="async" width="912" height="684"
                                                    src="https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_3996.jpg.webp"
                                                    alt="About" class="wp-image-1058" title="About 3"
                                                    srcset="https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_3996.jpg.webp 912w, https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_3996-300x225.jpg.webp 300w"
                                                    sizes="(max-width: 912px) 100vw, 912px"></noscript>
                                            <figcaption class="wp-element-caption">American Guests Ron &amp; Bob with us
                                                at <a
                                                    href="https://travelchinawith.me/attractions/yunnan/qujing/luoping-nine-dragon-jiulong-waterfalls/"
                                                    data-type="post" data-id="5167" target="_blank"
                                                    rel="noreferrer noopener">Jiulong Waterfall</a>, Mar 2009 | <a
                                                    href="https://travelchinawith.me/guests-world-wide-with-us/"
                                                    target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Check More Pics</a>
                                            </figcaption>
                                        </figure>
                                        <h3 class="wp-block-heading">Your Freedom &gt; Our Profit</h3>
                                        <p>We encourage customers to book their own hotels, flights, and train tickets,
                                            as we believe in offering you the freedom to choose, even at the cost of
                                            some profit. We may even suggest that you skip certain services if they are
                                            not necessary, such as a guide for airport/train station pick-up, unless you
                                            specifically need it.</p>
                                        <h3 class="wp-block-heading">100% No-Shopping Tours</h3>
                                        <p>Saw an unbelievably low-priced tour to China that caught your eye? <a
                                                href="https://travelchinawith.me/china-facts/china-group-tours-scams/"
                                                target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">It's highly likely to be a
                                                scam</a>. Many unscrupulous travel agencies are luring tourists by
                                            including hidden shopping stops in the itinerary, pressuring you to buy
                                            overpriced, low-quality goods, thus ruining your precious time, money, and
                                            experience! Please note: <strong>We guarantee 100% no-shopping
                                                tours</strong>. Our itineraries will not include any disguised shopping
                                            stops.</p>
                                        <h3 class="wp-block-heading">Understand You Like No Other</h3>
                                        <p>Since day one, we welcomed travelers from English-speaking countries and
                                            beyond—uniting adventurers from every corner of the world. Our guests spend
                                            their days immersed in China's wonders, side by side, giving us an unmatched
                                            insight into your tastes, habits, and desires.</p>
                                        <p> We deeply understand your habits and preferences without needing much
                                            explanation. This greatly enhances our communication efficiency and your
                                            comfort. You won't have to struggle to explain why you dislike one thing or
                                            prefer another—we already get it.</p>
                                        <h3 class="wp-block-heading">Timelier Service Efficiency</h3>
                                        <p>It's simple: which company is more efficient, one that handles 10,000
                                            tourists annually, or one that handles 3,000? The answer is obvious—larger
                                            organizations tend to be less efficient. With our smaller scale, we can
                                            provide more relaxed and focused attention to each customer, addressing
                                            their needs quickly.</p>
                                        <h3 class="wp-block-heading">Higher Service Quality</h3>
                                        <p>A smaller number of tourists allows us to maintain a more relaxed mindset and
                                            greater enthusiasm in handling each guest&#8217;s inquiries, rather than
                                            being overwhelmed with constant demands. Even if your inquiry isn't related
                                            to our business, we're always happy to help.</p>
                                        <figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="960"
                                                height="720"
                                                src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;960&#039;%20height=&#039;720&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20960%20720&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E"
                                                alt="About" class="wp-image-1882 perfmatters-lazy" title="About 4"
                                                data-src="https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1.jpg.webp"
                                                data-srcset="https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1.jpg.webp 960w, https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-300x225.jpg.webp 300w"
                                                data-sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /><noscript><img
                                                    decoding="async" width="960" height="720"
                                                    src="https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1.jpg.webp"
                                                    alt="About" class="wp-image-1882" title="About 4"
                                                    srcset="https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1.jpg.webp 960w, https://travelchinawith.me/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1-300x225.jpg.webp 300w"
                                                    sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px"></noscript>
                                            <figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Canadian Guests with us at <a
                                                    href="https://travelchinawith.me/attractions/yunnan/kunming/stone-forest-shilin/"
                                                    data-type="post" data-id="5009" target="_blank"
                                                    rel="noreferrer noopener">Stone Forest</a>, Aug 2024 | <a
                                                    href="https://travelchinawith.me/guests-world-wide-with-us/"
                                                    target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Check More Pics</a>
                                            </figcaption>
                                        </figure>
                                        <h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-learn-more-about-travel-china-with-me">Travel With Us!</h2>
                                        <p>Every great journey begins with a conversation.&nbsp;Whether you're drawn to
                                            our carefully crafted itineraries or dreaming of something uniquely yours,
                                            we're here to make it happen.</p>
                                        <p>Every great journey begins with a single step. Whether you're envisioning new
                                            horizons or seeking a personalized experience, let's take that step
                                            together!</p>
                                        <p>Hope we can meet each other someday in China like other modern smart
                                            travelers did.</p>
                                        <p>Welcome to China!</p>
                                        <p>Sincerely,<br />Dee</p>
                                    </div>
